How to Buy KAI

1

Create Your MetaMask Wallet

If you already have a web3 wallet, you can skip this step. If not, Metamask is recommended for security and simplicity. If on PC, you can download the Metamask Browser extension, and create your wallet. If on mobile, you will download the Metamask app. Both work, and its up to your preference which you choose.

2

SEND CRYPTO TO YOUR WALLET

Once youve got a wallet, youll need some crypto on it if youre not paying with a card. You can buy KAI during the presale with ETH, USDT, and BNB (BSC Chain). Use your favorite crypto exchange to buy some crypto, then make sure to send it to your wallet! 

3

BUY AND STAKE KAI

So youve got a web3 wallet with some crypto on it ready to buy. The next step is to connect your wallet to the website, using the Connect Wallet or Buy and Stake buttons. This will prompt a popup from your wallet. Sign, then youre ready to buy. Simply select the amount of KAI you want to Buy and Stake, and finalize the transaction!

4

Claim Your $KAI

Once the KAI presale is over, you can now collect your massive rewards. To claim your $KAI, you need to reconnect the SAME wallet you made the purchase with. It must be the same wallet address in order to properly claim. Now the fun KAIins, as KAI kicks doggie butt on the blockchain!
